This paper focuses on optimizing and parallelizing B-spline evaluations on multi/many-core shared memory processors, which falls under the category of computer engineering (cs.CE). The paper also discusses data layout transformation and cache reuse optimization, which are common topics in computer architecture (cs.AR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper employs performance analysis and modeling, which could fall under the categories of numerical analysis (cs.NA) and machine learning (cs.MS).
